cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely sub-category as the paper focuses on building an emotion classifier using deep learning and collecting facial emotion images. 
2. cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper mentions a game interface and game engine, which may involve graphics and visual elements. 
3. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible sub-category as the paper discusses a game-based data collection framework that involves user interaction. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible sub-category as the paper uses deep learning to build an emotion classifier. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible sub-category as the paper deals with collecting and analyzing multimedia data (facial emotion images).
